41
00:01:34,395 --> 00:01:36,462
Dogodilo se ubojstvo na privatnom otoku u blizini obale.

42
00:01:36,564 --> 00:01:37,908
Upravo idemo u marinu.

43
00:01:37,932 --> 00:01:38,730
Preuzmi brod.

44
00:01:38,833 --> 00:01:42,167
Žrtva je Serena Pendragon.

45
00:01:42,269 --> 00:01:43,802
Tridesetdevetogodišnji medij.

46
00:01:43,904 --> 00:01:46,238
Vidovnjak? Najstarija prijevara u knjizi.

47
00:01:46,340 --> 00:01:47,540
hajde Ti nisi vjernik.

48
00:01:47,608 --> 00:01:49,208
Vidovnjaci su najniži od najnižih.

49
00:01:49,310 --> 00:01:52,244
Oni vrebaju ljude u najgorim trenucima njihova života.

50
00:01:52,346 --> 00:01:54,246
A pošto si rekao privatni otok,

51
00:01:54,348 --> 00:01:56,281
Pretpostavljam da je marka bila bogata.

52
00:01:56,383 --> 00:01:58,283
Jeste li ikada čuli za obitelj Hawksmoor?

53
00:01:58,385 --> 00:02:00,586
Kao u Hawksmoor Frozen Seafood?

54
00:02:00,688 --> 00:02:01,587
Da, to je taj.

55
00:02:01,689 --> 00:02:03,288
Obožavam njihove pržene zalogaje od škampa.

56
00:02:03,390 --> 00:02:07,192
Mm. I meni također. Tako loše, ali tako dobro.

57
00:02:07,294 --> 00:02:09,661
Da, pa, osnivač, Alistair Hawksmoor,

58
00:02:09,763 --> 00:02:11,263
nestao prije sedam godina.

59
00:02:12,233 --> 00:02:13,132
Njegov čamac pronađen je kako pluta u moru,

60
00:02:13,234 --> 00:02:14,099
