Derwood čuvar. Sjajno ime.

84
00:03:16,397 --> 00:03:17,397
Vrlo sablasno.

85
00:03:18,332 --> 00:03:19,452
Možete li nas odvesti do tijela?

86
00:03:20,334 --> 00:03:21,334
Našli ste ga.

87
00:03:28,776 --> 00:03:29,875
