95
00:03:48,495 --> 00:03:49,294
Ujutro.

96
00:03:49,396 --> 00:03:50,195
Što si lutao okolo

97
00:03:50,297 --> 00:03:51,341
usred noći?

98
00:03:51,365 --> 00:03:53,632
Spremaju se opake oluje i mogli bismo izgubiti struju.

99
00:03:53,734 --> 00:03:55,534
Bio sam vani skupljajući dodatna drva.

100
00:03:55,636 --> 00:03:57,369
U redu, počnimo čistiti područje.

101
00:03:57,471 --> 00:03:59,204
Tražimo nož i otiske stopala.

102
00:04:00,774 --> 00:04:02,241
Iako sva ova mokra trava,

103
00:04:02,343 --> 00:04:03,486
Ne znam koliko otisaka...

104
00:04:03,510 --> 00:04:04,710
